class name shld begins with CAPITAL LETTER
don't use:ArrayList<String> name_array = new ArrayList<String>(10);
use:ArrayList<String> name_array = new ArrayList<>();
dont use half names for variables eg:num,i,a...
use iterate_variable,number,name_array
use constructors
you shld not get input as integer then string..........
eg:
int count=obj.nextInt();           //wrong
String firstname= obj.nextLine();
     int count=obj.nextInt();      //correct
     obj.nextLine();
     String firstname= obj.nextLine();
